title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 3 Day' game
title_page: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 3 Day' game
maintext:
BOISE, Idaho (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday afternoon’s drawing of the Idaho Lottery’s “Pick 3 Day” game were:
3-9-7
(three, nine, seven)
